Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.74,0:00:03.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's morning, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:11.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:14.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:16.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry about this every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:19.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:21.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,How about you? Is your body all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:26.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it's starting to get better,\Nbut it still screams everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:29.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please don't overwork yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:29.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:41.69,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.89,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,So you're here. Hurry and get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:44.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:00.63,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You're not holding the spanner right. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:02.38,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I showed you how it's done many times. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:03.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:06.05,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You're using too much adhesive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:08.38,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,And screw them in diagonal order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.01,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:10.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.51,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Concentrate. You'll get hurt if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:13.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:20.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:22.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:25.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I bought pork so you'll get your energy back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:27.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:31.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It'll be ready soon, so please sit and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:33.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The bath is ready, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:36.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:40.25,Default,TV,0,0,0,,I said that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.13,Default,TV,0,0,0,,No~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:42.96,Default,TV,0,0,0,,If you want it, go buy your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:44.17,Default,TV,0,0,0,,All right~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Are you sleepy, Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:49.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:55.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm being supported by Nagisa right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:02:00.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa worries and comes to see me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's all it takes me to keep\Nworking hard without giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:02.14,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 11
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:02.14,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}The Promised Founders Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:08.14,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Why do you do everything the hard way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:12.40,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It's easier to use both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.61,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Why don't you use your right hand more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:19.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, the way I do it is easier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.53,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Fine. It's not like you're doing things out of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.54,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Let's see, I would prefer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun. Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, what is it, Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:42.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I've been calling you for a while and you never answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry. I was thinking about work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:48.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing? {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:53.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're having tough days at work,\Nyet I'm bombarding you with conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:01.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Because you talk about lots of stuff, you're giving me a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Isn't it better for you to tell Yoshino-san that you have a bad right shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:14.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't. They might not let me work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:20.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even if Yoshino-san is all right with it,\Nthe manager might not be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:23.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That place pays pretty well for its size.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll be out on the street the moment I lose my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But please be careful of injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:30.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:36.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:39.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, aren't you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:47.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,After I leave, you're alone in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:52.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,When I think of that,\NI'm sometimes on the verge of crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Idiot. What's there to cry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You might be right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:01.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I go to bed as soon as I'm alone,\Nso there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry about a thing and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:07.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:23.73,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,We need picture proof at the end of construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.15,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.45,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Good work, Yoshino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:35.75,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kinoshita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.67,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Kinoshita-san, you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:44.55,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I used to work in the same office as Tomoya-kun's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.97,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I visited his home several times, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.97,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You've grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:54.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm surprised to see you in a place like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:58.14,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Since the last office closed,\NI transferred to the one I'm working in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.10,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Is your father doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:04.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm living alone now, so I haven't seen him recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:10.53,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,We work in various locations, so chance encounters like this happen once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.78,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It's moments like these that you feel how small the world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:17.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To me, it feels like the world just got bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.79,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You're looking at that pretty intently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:27.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Looking at this makes me think how buildings grow without me knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.59,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Things will change more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:36.27,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,When a new road opens, new office buildings and shops will stand alongside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.56,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,A big hospital will be built soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:44.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Though, I might not want to see too many changes too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you want to go somewhere next Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:57.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry. There's a mock exam on Sunday. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mock exam? I thought you weren't going to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:05.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Even so, I want to take the exam like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So, I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:12.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're kind of missing each other a lot these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:16.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. Do your best and get a good score.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:25.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So why do I have to come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.19,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't hate me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.03,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I just happen to have time today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:31.95,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Let's have some adult entertainment today, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Adult entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This is the toy store I visit regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're a regular?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.04,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,'ello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.60,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Stop moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:05.06,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Oh, he's got slow reflexes for someone you bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.90,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,He's an amateur, so give him a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There are pros at this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.90,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We'll call it draw for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:18.87,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So that makes it 123 wins,\N171 losses, and 32 draws for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is your idea of adult entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.16,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The real thing starts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.62,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey. Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.13,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:29.88,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.80,Default,Man,0,0,0,,A Bengal Giant Lizard, Mr. Lizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How very literal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:40.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We'll slip this down Sanae's back and surprise her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.64,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it makes my heart sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:49.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't you feel bad for Sanae-san? You should stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:54.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's stimulus that keeps the relationship between husband and wife fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.45,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You should remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is it really something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.99,San,San,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Tomoya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:06.96,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,By the way, Sanae, what was\Nyour least favorite animal again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:09.42,San,San,0,0,0,,The Bengal Giant Lizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So specific!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.00,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:15.17,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Look! There's a Bengal Giant Lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.63,San,San,0,0,0,,Wh-Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.93,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Look, it's gone over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:26.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh no! It went down your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.90,San,San,0,0,0,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.69,San,San,0,0,0,,Someone get it out please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:35.15,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Crap. That's more than a little stimulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.66,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You cheap bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:43.91,Default,Iso,0,0,0,,Wow, they're running faster than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Isogai-san. I'm sorry about the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:52.50,Default,Iso,0,0,0,,It's all right. Everyone around here says\Nevery day is entertaining thanks to those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:56.92,San,San,0,0,0,,Someone please get it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Wait, Sanae!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry, I need to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:04.18,Default,Iso,0,0,0,,Sure. Don't worry, I'll mind the store for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I was really surprised today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:14.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,When I got home, Dad, Mom, and you were all running.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:16.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san probably hates me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sure not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:22.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You get along very well with both Dad and Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:26.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I dropped the Bengal Giant Lizard down her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:31.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No one has ever run with Dad and Mom before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:36.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I think you really bonded with them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:44.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,By the way, Tomoya-kun. Do you know what happens two Sundays from today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Two Sundays from today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:49.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your birthday is December, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's the Founders Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:57.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The Theater Club is gone, but I want to have lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So if it's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sure. Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:06.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.21,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Today was a rough day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:23.34,Default,Man,0,0,0,,But I like since we get overtime. {Foreigner speaking non-fluent JP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.51,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Hey, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:26.93,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Organizing the stubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.77,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I'm having him help me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.89,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I can't make much progress alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.02,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm only organizing them by date.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.28,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Even so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.78,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I'd snap in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.41,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You want me to help you with this pile?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, that's the finished pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:51.62,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Forget it. You'll ruin it if you touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:56.54,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Hey, I was working as an accountant before I got laid off from my old job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:59.71,Default,Man,0,0,0,,No good to take rookie's job, Mister. {foreigner}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:04.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll be done soon, so please head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.97,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,If you say so. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.56,Default,Man,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.35,Default,Man,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.64,Default,Man,0,0,0,,See you, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.02,Default,Man,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.52,Default,Man,0,0,0,,It's a great help to have you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:23.24,Default,Man,0,0,0,,We were short on people despite\Nexpectations of getting a big job soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't do anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.24,Default,Man,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.87,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I hear he makes you do many tasks alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:34.04,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You'll probably end up coming on weekends more frequently, but keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:40.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Founders. Founders. Next weekend is the~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,~Founders Festival~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Apparently things will get busy from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:58.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I might not be able to go to the Founders Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:04.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry, when we're already losing our time together. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:12.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think it's great for work to be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:20.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's a bit of a shame, but I'm happy that you're working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:21.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.30,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Give me the cutters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:37.81,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Also, give me 210 mm of Sanshin's VVF cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.77,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Have the two ends stripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How much do you want it stripped?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:44.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll strip 2cm if it's thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.57,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Strip 4cm and it'll be multipurpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.57,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Make a note of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:49.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.24,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Have a 38 wrapper ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Protective tubing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Standard or extra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.62,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Let's go with extra just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.92,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,We don't want to see it catch fire later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.47,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Finish this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.76,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I'll go check the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:10.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.26,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Don't rush, and do it neatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.02,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I'll come back when I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:34.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. So I'd like a day off tomorrow if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:39.04,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I see. Don't worry. We don't have to give up our weekend tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.38,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,How's your right shoulder doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.96,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You can't lift your arm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.76,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I can tell just by looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.01,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,What will happen if I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.10,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You're not doing any procedures wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.19,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You were trying to overcome your handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:02.40,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Trying very hard to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:07.53,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,But difficult work will be coming in from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.07,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,If you think it's too much, then don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.61,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I'll cover you in those situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is that all right? Won't that only trouble you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:18.04,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,What can't be done will be covered by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.62,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,That's what work is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.88,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I'll have you do things I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:24.50,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,That's the way it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:31.88,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Basically, make sure you don't screw anything up and worry your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:49.32,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Man, everyone went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:54.95,Default,Man,0,0,0,,A job got slipped out of the pile by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:55.95,Default,Man,0,0,0,,It's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.41,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Do you think you can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If it's this, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's the same thing I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:07.13,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Really? Then sorry, but can you go do it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,By myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.42,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I've got other things to do and can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.26,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I'll give you a ride to the place, so please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.89,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I'll come pick you up later, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:16.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:32.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:36.78,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Manager gave me a call, so I ran back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.03,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Did you manage it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.92,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Have you checked the junctions? {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:49.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. At each circuit and the entire thing at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.88,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Did you strip the insulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. And I measured them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.06,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.56,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It's late already, so let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:03.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:10.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll be at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. We'll meet at the gate later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:14.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:25.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:30.17,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Okazaki-kun. Do you know what happened on-site yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:38.26,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Yoshino just called in and said he noticed a mistake, so he'd go fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.72,Default,Man,0,0,0,,He won't tell me even when I asked him to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:44.39,Default,Man,0,0,0,,So I thought you might know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.94,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Okazaki! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:52.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"What"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If I had done it properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:18:59.99,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:00.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:04.04,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I noticed it after you went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:07.62,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,But it was already nighttime,\Nso I rolled the work over to today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:10.58,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It was my mistake for not noticing your mistake on-site.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.00,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You have a promise with Nagisa-san, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.17,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Hurry and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Please let me take responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:17.55,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.98,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Bring up 6m of 25 low-pressure extension cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:29.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.23,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:55.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:57.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.55,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So you were at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I had a feeling that you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:09.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're drenched in sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.11,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You've done nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Will you eat these with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Let's eat as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:34.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:50.60,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Mr. Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.64,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I heard you had big job yesterday. {foreigner}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:54.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.15,Default,Man,0,0,0,,We heard from Yoshino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.32,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You skipped a date with\Nyour girl and came to work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.95,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You should have said so, and I would have gone for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.32,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.91,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to give you overtime for the weekend work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:11.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Um, I came thinking I'd get yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.54,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Everyone makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.13,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,What's important is how to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.80,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You did your best and we didn't cause any trouble to the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:24.05,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Don't make the same mistake, and that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:32.02,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,If you're feeling sorry, then handle the mistakes the juniors you'll eventually have will make.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:34.44,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's{\i0\fscx30}{\r} your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:35.98,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.48,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:46.57,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I think last one word not needed. {foreigner}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.74,Default,Man,0,0,0,,All right, enough talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.12,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.79,Default,All,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.08,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Ah, Okazaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.29,Default,Man,0,0,0,,It's finally done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.46,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
