Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:46.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think you look kinder now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:51.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I always thought things like that were annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.11,0:23:55.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And I say this when at school, I stuck my nose into other people's business so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:24:00.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think you should choose the path you think is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:08.83,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Don't lose track of what's important to you.
